@startuml
[*] --> State1: Order
State1 --> State2: Arrival [Upon arrival]
State2 --> State3: Preparation
State3 --> State4: Operations [Scheduled flights]
State4 --> State5: Maintenance [No scheduled flights or maintenance required]
State5 --> State6: Preparation [After checking and servicing]
State6 --> State7: Operations
State7 --> State8: Withdrawn [Permanently withdrawn from service]

@enduml
